data.description: Lovely Rancho Sahuarita home range priced from $305,000 to $320,000. At top end of range, Seller will give a credit towards closing costs or pay down a portion of the solar loan. Enjoy this move-in ready 4 bedroom, 2 bath home with an extended length 2-car garage and newer HVAC system. The living space is large and flexible with 9' ceilings, a remodeled kitchen with SS appliances, surround sound speakers and more! Backyard is fully finished! The community has so much to offer, and the neighbors are festive and friendly! Enjoy neighborhood gatherings, a water park, full gym, pools, basketball courts, fishing, and more! Solar loan balance is less than $15k with Titan Solar. Solar covers most of electricity use. Come. See. Stay!
